OL,3,CCarlisle care home worker avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter stealing #15,000 from residents
OL,6,FA Carlisle woman has avoided jail
OL,7,Fafter stealing thousands of pounds
OL,8,Ffrom two residents of the city care
OL,9,Fhome where she was working.
OL,11,FThirty-year-old Jessica Gregson
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to two offences on 4
OL,13,FJuly 2025
OL,15,FOne involves fraud by dishonestly
OL,16,Fmaking a false representation, namely
OL,17,Fthat she had permission to use a bank
OL,18,Fcard in a man's name.
OL,20,FA second crime relates to the theft of
OL,21,F#9,414.80 from the man.
