OL,3,CCarlisle care home worker avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter stealing #15,000 from residents
OL,6,FGregson's offending occurred during a
OL,7,Fperiod of nine months, between 3 April
OL,8,F2023 and 8 January 2024 while working
OL,9,Fat Pennine Lodge Care Home.
OL,11,FEarlier this year, Gregson pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to charges of fraud and theft
OL,13,Frelating to a different care home
OL,14,Fresident.
OL,16,FShe admitted using that woman's card
OL,17,Fwithout permission and stealing
OL,18,F#6,140.50 from her between 1 December
OL,19,F2023 and 7 February the following year.
