OL,3,CCarlisle care home worker avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter stealing #15,000 from residents
OL,6,FIt was when Gregson appeared at
OL,7,FCarlisle Crown Court in May in
OL,8,Frelation to those original two charges
OL,9,Fthat a judge learned there may be a
OL,10,Fsecond victim. Relatives of that man `
OL,11,Fwho has since died ` were present in
OL,12,Fcourt on that occasion.
OL,14,FThe case was adjourned at that stage
OL,15,Ffor further enquiries to be made. As a
OL,16,Fresult, two additional charges were
OL,17,Fbrought.
