OL,3,CCarlisle care home worker avoids jail
OL,4,Cafter stealing #15,000 from residents
OL,6,FToday, back at the Crown Court, she
OL,7,Fwas given a 24 month suspended
OL,8,Fsentence and must complete 200 hours
OL,9,Fon unpaid work.
OL,11,FRecorder William Beardmore told
OL,12,FGregson in court: "You targeted two
OL,13,Fvulnerable people in your care and you
OL,14,Fabused your position of trust."
